data.title: Baby Name Indian Boy
data.meta_description:
Baby Name Indian Boy - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides a long list of Indian baby names for boys beginning with letters A through G. Some of the names and their meanings include:

Abhay - fearless. Abhijit - one who is victorious. Akash - sky. Amar - immortal. Amit - endless. Devdas - servant of Lord. Dhananjay - one who wins wealth. Ganesh - son of Lord Shiva, the elephant-headed God. Gaurav - honor, respect, pride.
